Disable all telemetry and crash reporting by default

Forces telemetry level to OFF, disables crash reporting, and redirects
telemetry endpoints (data.microsoft.com) to 0.0.0.0 to prevent any data
from being sent even if settings are misconfigured.

Note: when pulling a new change from upstream, make sure to replace all
.data.microsoft.com with 0.0.0.0. Otherwise the OSS will still ping
Microsoft, even if the telemetry is set to OFF.
See: https://github.com/VSCodium/vscodium/issues/26

